name: Windjinn
printed_effect:
When this Windjinn receives 1 or more {wind} you
can name a card, then Foretell 3. If 1 or more
cards with that name are Foretold this way, you
may add 1 to your hand and Special Ascend this
Windjinn to Tornadjinn from your hand or deck.
